      "text": "# Registration of membership\nWhen a stranger who is not in the wikiverse finds one of my wiki.cafe sites, can they create a wiki .cafe site directly from that location?\n- They will need to be offered membership in wiki.cafe. \n- They will need an oAuth login. \n\n"
