      "text": "wiki.cafe will need:\n- a **member-registration** process (triggered by an OpenCollective subscription)\n- which issues **oAuth login credentials** and which\n- **pops up** whenever a reader of a wiki.cafe site follows the standard protocol of wiki, which is to spin-up a site on the same server as the site they first encountered, by entering a new url under the same domain.\n\n"
